%22%3Edisaster%20at%20the%20Titanic%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20wonder%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-icon-of-the-seas-titanic-comparison-photos-2023-7%5C%22%3EIcon%20of%20the%20Seas%3C%2Fa%3E%20met%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20the%20storied%20ocean%20liner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Icon%20of%20the%20Seas%20is%20currently%20set%20to%20sail%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20meaning%20it%20won't%20be%20encountering%20ice.%20But%20even%20if%20in%20the%20future%20its%20used%20in%20an%20area%20in%20which%20there%20could%20be%20ice%2C%20it's%20still%20incredibly%20rare%20for%20a%20cruise%20ship%20today%20to%20strike%20an%20iceberg.%20It's%20not%20impossible%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20in%20an%20incident%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2007%2F11%2F24%2Fworld%2Famericas%2F24ship.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bmodern%20Titanic%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20small%20cruise%20ship%20struck%20ice%2C%20causing%20a%20fist-sized%20hole%20that%20let%20water%20into%20the%20engine%20room%20and%20caused%20the%20power%20to%20fail.%20The%20154%20people%20on%20board%20had%20to%20evacuate%20on%20lifeboats%20and%20rafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfEA4Wcx_1f8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorwegian%20Cruise%20Line%20ship%20hit%20an%20iceberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20traveling%20through%20dense%20fog%20near%20Alaska%2C%20causing%20enough%20damage%20to%20shorten%20the%20voyage%20and%20cancel%20another%20so%20it%20could%20undergo%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20neither%20was%20a%20catastrophe%20of%20Titanic%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruise%20industry%20expert%20Stewart%20Chiron%2C%20better%20known%20as%20The%20Cruise%20Guy%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3