20consulting%20with%20Einstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20Project%20was%20officially%20created%20in%20August%201942%2C%20months%20after%20the%20US%20entered%20the%20war.%20The%20years-long%20program%20developed%20the%20world's%20first%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20which%20were%20dropped%20on%20Japanese%20cities%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20in%201945.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWoe%20is%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Einstein%20said%20after%20learning%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20AMNH.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20expressed%20remorse%20for%20recommending%20that%20the%20US%20start%20its%20own%20nuclear%20program%2C%20telling%20Newsweek%2C%20%26quot%3BHad%20I%20known%20that%20the%20Germans%20would%20not%20succeed%20in%20developing%20an%20atomic%20bomb%2C%20I%20would%20have%20done%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESzilard%20and%20his%20fellow%20Hungarian-born%20physicist%20Eugene%20Wigner%20both%20expressed%20their%20agreement%20with%20Einstein's%20statements%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1964%2F08%2F02%2Farchives%2Fthe-einstein-letter-that-started-it-all-a-message-to-president.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20Project%20is%20the%20center%20of%20a%20new%20biopic%20from%20director%20Christopher%20Nolan.%20%26quot%3BOppenheimer%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20chronicles%20the%20physicist's%20work%20developing%20the%20nukes%20and%20stars%20Cillian%20Murphy%2C%20releases%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-einstein-didnt-join-manhattan-project-oppenheimer-atomic-bomb-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689802469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649d4552ca78800019708769%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-einstein-di