ngouda-patil-rushed-to-hospital-amid-protests-in-karnataka-assembly-4222973%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-bjp-mla-basangouda-patil-rushed-to-hospital-amid-protests-in-karnataka-assembly-4222973%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-bjp-mla-basangouda-patil-rushed-to-hospital-amid-protests-in-karnataka-assembly-4222973%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jason%20Aldean%3A%20US%20country%20star%20denies%20new%20music%20video%20is%20'pro-lynching'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689788284000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10663%2Fproduction%2F_130417176_gettyimages-1497578229.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66248807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jason%20Aldean%20defends%20his%20song%20as%20it%20is%20yanked%20by%20Country%20Music%20Television%20and%20Sheryl%20Crow%20attacks%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A966%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66248807%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66248807.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66248807.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20INDIA%2C%20The%20Death%20Of%20UPA%2C%20And%20A%202018%20Reminder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20too%20long%20ago%20that%20the%20Left-leaning%20intellectuals%20and%20some%20'centrist'%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20talked%20about%20%26quot%3Btwo%20India%26quot%3B%20--%20an%20'India'%20shining%20for%20a%20select%20few%20and%20the%20'Bharat'%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20afflicted%20by%20poverty%20and%20backwardness.%20When%20that%20%26quot%3Btwo%20India%26quot%3B%20theory%20drew%20criticism%2C%20it%20was%20buried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangh%20Parivar%20and%20its%20sympathisers%20loved%20to%20call%20our%20nation%20Bharat%2C%20while%20others%20preferred%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20significant%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20named%20his%20recent%20countrywide%20campaign%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%20It%2C%20therefore%2C%20sounded%20a%20bit%20ironic%20when%20the%20Congress-hosted%2026-party%20conclave%20in%20Bengaluru%20named%20the%20alliance%20INDIA.%20The%20logic%20offered%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20was%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20resonated%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20That%20was%20the%20origin%20of%20INDIA%20as%20an%20acronym%20for%20'Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20perhaps%20didn't%20think%20of%20this%20counter-argument%20--%20Did%20the%20ancient%20name%20Bharat%20not%20resonate%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20even%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20much-hyped%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20should%20the%2026-party%20alliance%20lose%20the%20election%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20and%20NDA%20win%2C%20again%3F%20Going%20by%20the%20current%20popularity%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20it%20is%20a%20big%20possibility%20next%20year.%20Imagine%20then%2C%20how%20media%2C%20particularly%20the%20Western%20Media%2C%20would%20fancy%20a%20banner%20headline%20like%20-%20%26quot%3BModi%20wins%2C%20INDIA%20loses%26quot%3B.%20Will%20that%20look%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20India%20Gandhi%20era%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20was%20Indira%20and%20Indira%20was%20India%26quot%3B.%20Decades%20later%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20in%20no%20position%20to%20put%20up%20a%20real%20electoral%20challenge%2C%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20its%20chairperson.%20She%20was%20an%20extra-constitutional%20authority%20for%2010%20years%20of%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20UPA%20government%2C%20with%20great%20power%20and%20no%20responsibility.%20Even%20in%20parliamentary%20protocol%20she%20enjoyed%20special%20status%20as%20the%20UPA%20chairperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Congress-hosted%20Bengaluru%20meet%20saw%20the%20burial%20of%20UPA.%20Gone%20is%20the%20primacy%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%20in%20alternate%20political%20formation.%20The%20nomenclature%20for%20the%20Opposition%20grouping%2C%20INDIA%2C%20was%20proposed%20by%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20at%20the%20meeting.%20It%20now%20transpires%20that%20the%20new%20nomenclature%20was%20brainchild%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20with%20due%20deliberations%20with%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20without%20taking%20into%20confidence%20a%20host%20of%20other%20leaders%20present%20there%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20for%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikes%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20so%20far%20was%20acting%20on%20behalf%20of%20Congress%20party%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20leaders%20like%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20as%20chief%20architect%20of%20opposition%20unity%2C%20was%20taken%20by%20surprise%20when%20the%20name%20INDIA%20was%20proposed%20by%20the%20TMC%20chief.%20Nitish%20and%20some%20others%20opposed%20the%20idea%20but%20were%20overruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20will%20be%20hosted%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20The%20alliance%20will%20have%20a%20secretariat%20of%20its%20own%20with%2011%20steering%20committee%20members.%20All%20that%20is%20good%20but%20who%20will%20be%20convenor%2C%20if%20at%20all%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Congress%20leader%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20not%20discussed%20in%20the%20meeting.%20He%20even%20pontificated%20on%20why%20a%20convenor%20was%20even%20needed.%20The%20issue%20was%20only%20in%20the%20media%2C%20it%20was%20a%20non-issue%20for%20them.%20Basically%2C%20the%20host%20is%20the%20convenor%2C%20wherever%20the%20meeting%20is%20held%2C%20like%20musical%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20last%20month%20hosted%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%26quot%3B%20opposition%20meet%20in%20Patna.%20His%20stamp%20was%20all%20over%20the%20meet.%20Yet%20at%20Bengaluru%2C%20no%20one%20was%20talking%20about%20him%20-%20not%20any%20party%20or%20the%20media%20-%20except%20for%20hoardings%20targeting%20him%20as%20%26quot%3BUnstable%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate%26quot%3B%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%20He%20was%20not%20on%20the%20dais%20with%20some%20four%20dozen%20leaders%20in%20the%20combined%20press%20conference.%20No%20one%20cared%20to%20ask%20why%20he%20was%20not%20there.%20Nor%20did%20the%20leaders%20who%20addressed%20the%20media%20conference%20mention%20him.%20Though%20Kharge%20said%20some%20of%20our%20friends%20had%20to%20leave%20as%20they%20had%20earlier%20flights.%20What%20Kharge%20didn't%20tell%20was%20that%20most%20of%20his%20friends%20were%20flying%20in%20private%20chartered%20flights.%20Even%20otherwise%20they%20very%20well%20knew%20the%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20politics%2C%20Charcha%2C%20Parcha%20aur%20Photoplays%20an%20important%20part%20in%20communicating%20a%20message%20to%20the%20public%20at%20large%2C%20and%20maintaining%20relevance.%20In%20contrast%20to%20Patna%2C%20where%20Nitish%20Kumar%20invited%20all%20leaders%20(where%20a%20sulking%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20left%20before%20start%20of%20press%20conference)%20to%20speak%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%20only%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20were%20invited%20to%20speak.%20The%20media%20was%20asked%20to%20pose%20questions%20only%20to%20Kharge%2C%20that%20too%20only%20four%20or%20five%20straight%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20arguments%20and%20agenda%20revolved%20around%20five%20abstract%20philosophical%20concepts%20-%201.%20They%20have%20come%20together%20to%20save%20the%20country.%202.%20They%20have%20come%20together%20to%20save%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country.%203.%20They%20have%20come%20together%20to%20save%20the%20Constitution.%204.%20Modi%20has%20destroyed%20the%20country%20and%20has%20brought%20disrepute%20to%20the%20country.%205.%20They%20have%20to%20anticipate%20popular%20will%20and%20save%20the%20country%20from%20Modi's%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20seemed%20to%20be%20completely%20oblivious%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20per%20the%20United%20Nation's%20Multi-Dimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20(MPI)%2C%20a%20tenth%20of%20the%20population%20or%20around%2013.5%20crore%20people%20have%20been%20brought%20out%20of%20poverty.%20There%20is%20a%20rising%20middle%20and%20neo-middle%20class%2C%20so%20is%20a%20young%20aspirational%20India.%20The%20opposition%20coalition%20INDIA%20has%20nothing%20to%20offer%20to%20them%20other%20than%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20complete%20disregard%20to%20the%20wishes%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20bent%20over%20backwards%20to%20accommodate%20the%20whims%20of%20Kejriwal%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20Naturally%2C%20Mamata%20and%20Kejriwal%2C%20in%20comparison%20to%20all%20other%20leaders%20present%2C%20appeared%20buoyant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20politics%20is%20a%20game%20of%20numbers%2C%20then%20consider%20this.%20Just%20as%20the%20INDIA%20meeting%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20ended%2C%20PM%20Modi%20led%20a%2038-party%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%20meeting%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20with%20the%20tagline%20%26quot%3B25%20years%20of%20service%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlashback%20to%202018.%20Almost%20the%20same%20number%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20gathered%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20a%20show%20of%20strength%20and%20unity%20at%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Congress-Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689787320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fj5iaj1lg_opposition-bengaluru-pti_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-india-the-death-of-upa-and-a-2018-reminder-4223702%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20wasn't%20too%20long%20ago%20that%20the%20Left-leaning%20intellectuals%20and%20some%20'centrist'%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20talked%20about%20%26quot%3Btwo%20India%26quot%3B%20--%20an%20'India'%20shining%20for%20a%20select%20few%20and%20the%20'Bharat'%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20afflicted%20by%20poverty%20and%20backwardness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-india-the-death-of-upa-and-a-2018-reminder-4223702%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-india-the-death-of-upa-and-a-2018-reminder-4223702%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-india-the-death-of-upa-and-a-2018-reminder-4223702%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leader%20of%20Russian%20mutiny%20'reappears%20in%20public'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689786939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F152EB%2Fproduction%2F_130436768_c90ce103-37af-4c68-b24f-574ae251fadc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66249551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20footage%20appear