e%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoksha%20has%20also%20assisted%20in%20educational%20sessions%20for%20deprived%20schoolchildren%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20receive%20the%20Points%20of%20Light%20award.%20I%20hope%20both%20children%20and%20adults%20get%20to%20understand%20that%20caring%20for%20the%20planet%20and%20its%20people%20and%20making%20small%20changes%20to%20everyday%20life%20should%20not%20be%20just%20for%20a%20few.%20It%20is%20just%20like%20brushing%20our%20teeth%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20brush%20our%20teeth%20to%20care%20for%20them%20and%20avoid%20pain%3B%20similarly%20we%20can%20take%20care%20of%20the%20planet%20not%20for%20anyone%20else%2C%20but%20just%20us%2C%20to%20be%20safe.%20Each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20us%20can%20do%20small%20things%20in%20our%20own%20lives%2C%20work%20and%20community%20to%20combat%20the%20big%20challenges%20such%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20pollution%2C%20poverty%20and%20inequality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%2C%20Ragini%20G%20Roy%20and%20Sourav%20Roy%2C%20said%20their%20daughter's%20efforts%20prove%20that%20even%20the%20youngest%20in%20society%20have%20a%20role%20to%20play%20in%20combatting%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Downing%20Street%2C%20the%20Points%20of%20Light%20awards%20recognise%20outstanding%20people%20whose%20service%20is%20making%20a%20difference%20in%20their%20communities%20and%20whose%20story%20can%20inspire%20others%20towards%20innovative%20solutions%20to%20social%20challenges%20in%20their%20own%20communities%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689785520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F8ijeqggo_moksha-roy_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%