Kuki%20Women%20Paraded%20Naked%3B%20One%20Was%20Allegedly%20Gang-Raped%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20video%20that%20is%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%2C%20showing%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%2C%20is%20from%20May%204%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20ongoing%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20began%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20in%20B%20Phainom%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20on%20May%204.%20One%20of%20the%20women%20was%20gang-raped%2C%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20shows%20several%20men%2C%20apparently%20Meiteis%2C%20walking%20alongside%20the%20two%20women%20as%20they%20are%20led%20into%20some%20fields.%20The%20video%20shows%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20men%20groping%20the%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20zero%20FIR%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Saikul%20police%2C%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%2C%20on%20May%2018.%20It%20was%20forwarded%20to%20the%20Nongpok%20Sekmai%20police%20station%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%20While%C2%A0an%20FIR%20is%20usually%20restricted%20by%20jurisdiction%2C%20a%20zero%20FIR%20can%20be%20filed%20in%20any%20police%20station.%20After%20registering%20the%20Zero%20FIR%2C%20the%20police%20station%20transfers%20it%20to%20the%20one%20that%20has%20the%20jurisdiction%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20then%20supposed%20to%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20regular%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zero%20FIR%20has%20charges%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%20against%20%E2%80%9Cunknown%20miscreants%E2%80%9D%20numbering%20%E2%80%9C800-1%2C000%E2%80%9D.%20%C2%A0The%20complaint%20filed%20against%20the%20incident%20claims%20that%20these%20men%20are%20suspected%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmembers%20of%20Meitei%20Youth%20Organisations%2C%20Meetei%20Leepun%2C%20Kangleipak%20Kanba%20Lup%2C%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20World%20Meitei%20Council%2C%20Schedule%20Tribe%20Demand%20Committee%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mob%20is%20accused%20of%20burning%20down%20houses%20in%20the%20B%20Phainom%20village%2C%20and%20accosting%20a%20group%20of%20five%20people%20who%20were%20fleeing.%20There%20were%20two%20men%20and%20three%20women%20in%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20group%20was%20%E2%80%9Csnatched%20away%20from%20the%20custody%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20police%20team%20from%20the%20Nongpok%20Sekmai%20police%20station%20near%20Toubul%20(Sekmai%20khunou)%20%E2%80%9Cabout%202%20km%20from%20Nongpok%20Sekmai%20PS%20and%20about%203%20km%20from%2033%20AR%20Somrei%20Post%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20men%20was%20killed%20immediately%20by%20the%20mob%2C%20which%20then%20forced%20all%20the%20women%20to%20strip.%20One%20woman%2C%20in%20her%2020s%2C%20was%20gang-raped%20and%20the%20other%20two%20women%20escaped.%20When%20the%20brother%20of%20the%20woman%20who%20was%20being%20raped%20tried%20to%20stop%20the%20assault%2C%20he%20was%20also%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1681711021126189081%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20making%20%E2%80%9Call-out%20effort%E2%80%9D%20to%20arrest%20the%20culprits%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20incident.%20The%20police%20said%20that%20a%20case%20of%20abduction%2C%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20was%20registered%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20tribal%20groups%2C%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Chorrifying%20ordeal%20suffered%20by%20these%20innocent%20women%20is%20amplified%20by%20the%20perpetrators%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20share%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20video%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20on%20social%20media%E2%80%9D.%20It%20vehemently%20condemned%20the%20sickening%20act%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%2C%20apart%20from%20statutory%20bodies%20like%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20should%20take%20cognizance%20of%20the%20offence%20and%20take%20all%20necessary%20measures%20to%20bring%20justice%20to%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20Tipra%20Motha%2C%20Pradyot%20Manikya%20Deb%20Barma%2C%20tweeted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdisturbing%E2%80%9D%20video%20shows%20there%20is%20total%20breakdown%20in%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20there.%20%E2%80%9CHate%20has%20won%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPradyotManikya%2Fstatus%2F1681665076573478912%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAttention%20India.%20The%20modesty%20of%20two%20tribal%20women%20from%20Manipur%20were%20outraged%20on%204th%20May.%20They%20were%20paraded%20naked%2C%20fondled%20and%20beaten%20in%20full%20public%20glare.%20A%20disturbing%20video%20taken%20by%20a%20perpetrator%20leaked%20and%20got%20viral%20today.%20This%20breaks%20all%20level%20of%20humanity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manipur%20resident%20and%20journalist%20Hoihnu%20Hauzel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhoihnu%2Fstatus%2F1681638380550127616%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClashes%20between%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20Kuki%20community%20have%20been%20ongoing%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%203.%20The%20violence%20began%20after%20a%20solidarity%20march%20held%20by%20tribal%20groups%20against%20the%20demand%20to%20grant%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20So%20far%2C%20at%20least%20140%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20many%20more%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20nearly%2050%2C000%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kuki%20groups%20have%20accused%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%2C%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwatch-manipur-violence-bjp-mla-paolienlal-haokip%5C%22%3Estoking%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20opposition%20parties%20have%20also%20slammed%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Fnational-politics%2Fopposition-parties-slam-pm-narendra-modi-for-stoic-silence-on-manipur-1229582.html%23%5C%22%3Esilence%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689784748000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20occurred%20in%20B%20Phainom%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20on%20May%204%2C%20one%20day%20after%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%20began.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bollywood%20actresses%20who%20dared%20to%20bare%20it%20all%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689784484000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101965589%2Cimgsize-54722.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Ffrom-radhika-to-zeenat-bollywood-actresses-who-dared-to-bare-it-all-on-the-big-screen%2Fphotostory%2F101965589.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101965589.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERadhika%20Apte%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20Disha%20Patani%2C%20Sunny%20Leone%2C%20Mandakini%20and%20other%20Bollywood%20actresses%20have%20dared%20to%20bare%20it%20all%20on%20the%20big%20screen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Ffrom-radhika-to-zeenat-bollywood-actresses-who-dared-to-bare-it-all-on-the-big-screen%2Fphotostory%2F101965589.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teen%2C%20Infant%20Drown%20In%20Swollen%20Drains%20Near%20Mumbai%20As%20Rain%20Batters%20City%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rains%20lashed%20Mumbai%20and%20adjoining%20Thane%20and%20Palghar%20districts%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20disrupting%20suburban%20rail%20traffic%20and%20causing%20water-logging%20in%20low-lying%20areas%20from%20where%20people%20were%20evacuated%2C%20while%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20drowned%20in%20a%20swollen%20drain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20four-month-old%20infant%20slipped%20out%20of%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20woman%20walking%20on%20railway%20tracks%20and%20fell%20into%20a%20nullah%20between%20Thakurli%20and%20Kalyan%20stations%20in%20Thane%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Railway's%20suburban%20train%20services%20on%20the%20Kalyan-Badlapur%20stretch%20in%20Thane%20district%20were%20restored%20after%20seven%20hours%2C%20officials%20said.%20Services%20on%20the%20Kalyan-Kasara%20route%20were%20up%20and%20running%20after%20nearly%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EServices%20between%20Badlapur%20and%20Ambarnath%20were%20stopped%20at%2011.05%20hours%20due%20to%20waterlogging%20which%20disrupted%20the%20movement%20of%20trains%20from%20Kalyan%20to%20Karjat.%20%26quot%3BPoint%20failures%26quot%3B%20between%20Kalyan%20and%20Kasara%20prompted%20railway%20officials%20to%20stop%20the%20services%20on%20the%20stretch%20at%20around%202.40%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disruptions%20caused%20inconvenience%20to%20thousands%20of%20commuters.%20Since%20trains%20crawled%20or%20stood%20still%20on%20tracks%2C%20several%20commuters%20were%20seen%20walking%20on%20rail%20lines%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rajnish%20Kumar%20Goyal%2C%20divisional%20manager%20of%20Central%20Railway's%20Mumbai%20division%2C%20the%20Ambarnath-Badlapur%20stretch%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Kalyan-Karjat%20section%2C%20was%20opened%20for%20traffic%20around%206%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Down%20(Karjat-bound)%20line%20was%20restored%20first%20followed%20by%20the%20Up%20line%20(CSMT-bound)%20about%20half%20an%20hour%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20they%20had%20stopped%20the%20services%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure%20as%20water%20was%20flowing%208%20inches%20above%20the%20track%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaterlogged%20tracks%20and%20technical%20failures%20had%20prompted%20railway%20authorities%20to%20cancel%20several%20suburban%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommuters%20complained%20of%20bunching%20of%20trains%2C%20due%20to%20which%20several%20of%20them%20jumped%20onto%20the%20tracks%20and%20walked%20to%20reach%20their%20desired%20destination%20or%20next%20station.%20They%20also%20complained%20of%20heavy%20rush%20at%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Railway%20said%20it%20had%20diverted%20some%20mail%20and%20express%20trains%20via%20the%20Diva-Panvel-Karjat%20route%20and%20Daund-Manmad%20route%2C%20besides%20short-terminating%20and%20cancelling%20a%20few%20trains%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20announced%20a%20holiday%20for%20all%20schools%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane%2C%20Raigad%20and%20Palghar%20districts%20on%20Thursday%20(July%2020)%20due%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%2C%20in%20a%20circular%20issued%20late%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20said%20schools%20(those%20having%20classes%20from%20nursery%20to%2012)%20will%20remain%20closed%20in%20the%20city%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20showers%20also%20pounded%20Thane%20and%20Palghar%20districts%2C%20causing%20water-logging%20in%20many%20localities%20following%20which%20more%20than%20250%20families%20from%20low-lying%20areas%20in%20Thane%20were%20shifted%20to%20safer%20places%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalghar%20Collector%20Govind%20Bodke%20declared%20a%20holiday%20for%20all%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20the%20district%20on%20July%2020%20(Thursday)%20in%20view%20of%20a%20heavy%20rain%20alert.%20The%20collector%20also%20advised%20citizens%20to%20avoid%20stepping%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20if%20it%20is%20not%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2024%20hours%20ended%20at%208.30%20am%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Thane%20city%20received%2090.08%20mm%20of%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20rivers%2C%20including%20the%20Ulhas%20(Thane)%2C%20Amba%2C%20Savitri%20and%20Patalganga%20(in%20neighbouring%20Raigad)%20were%20in%20spate%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20NDRF%20(National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force)%20was%20dispatched%20to%20rescue%20some%20people%20trapped%20in%20Kalyan%20township%20as%20water%20from%20the%20swollen%20Ulhas%20river%20flooded%20some%20localities%2C%20a%20district%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20areas%20in%20Bhiwandi%20city%2C%20also%20in%20Thane%20district%2C%20were%20marooned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20200%20families%20from%20Sonivali%20and%20Hendrepada%20in%20Badlapur%20town%20of%20Thane%20were%20shifted%20to%20safer%20places%20following%20heavy%20downpour%20and%20flooding%20in%20those%20areas%2C%20District%20Information%20Officer%20Nandkumar%20Waghmare%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2060%20families%20from%20Morya%20Nagar%20in%20Kalyan%20taluka%20and%20inmates%20of%20a%20senior%20citizens'%20home%20in%20Ambarnath%20town%20in%20Thane%20district%20were%20also%20shifted%20to%20safer%20places%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20the%20Thane%20district%20headquarters%20said%20the%20Amba%20river%20in%20Nagotane%2C%20Savitri%20in%20Mahad%2C%20Patalganga%20in%20Lohap%2C%20and%20Ulhas%20river%20in%20Jambulpada%20have%20crossed%20the%20danger%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kundalika%20river%20in%20Dolvahal%2C%20Ulhas%20in%20Badlapur%2C%20and%20Kalu%20in%20Titwala%20have%20crossed%20the%20warning%20level%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20some%20bridges%20were%20inundated%20between%20Rayte%20and%20Dahagaon%20(over%20Ulhas%20river)%2C%20on%20the%20road%20leading%20to%20Chikle%20village%20(over%20Kalu%20river)%2C%20and%20over%20the%20Murbadi%20river%20in%20Murbad%2C%20a%20district%20administration%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20areas%20in%20Vasai%20were%20water-logged%20and%20teams%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%2C%20police%20and%20revenue%20department%20were%20carrying%20out%20rescue%20and%20relief%20operations%2C%20Palghar%20disaster%20management%20cell%20chief%20Vivekanand%20Kadam%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20four-month-old%20infant%20slipped%20out%20of%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20woman%20walking%20on%20railway%20tracks%20and%20fell%20into%20a%20nullah%20between%20Thakurli%20and%20Kalyan%20stations%20in%20Thane%20district%20as%20heavy%20rains%20disrupted%20local%20train%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Fire%20Brigade%20official%20said%20they%20have%20received%20a%20distress%20call%20about%20a%20child%20falling%20into%20the%20nullah%20along%20the%20railway%20track%20in%20Thane%20district%20and%20are%20launching%20an%20operation%20to%20trace%20the%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhiwandi%20city%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20drowned%20in%20a%20swollen%20drain%20while%20her%2012-year-old%20brother%20was%20rescued%20by%20people%2C%20a%20civic%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20in%20the%20afternoon%20when%2