0the%20weather%20office%2C%20some%20areas%20of%20Mumbai%20is%20likely%20to%20witness%20heavy%20rain%20tomorrow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-schools-in-mumbai-to-be-closed-tomorrow-due-to-heavy-rain-4223096%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-schools-in-mumbai-to-be-closed-tomorrow-due-to-heavy-rain-4223096%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-schools-in-mumbai-to-be-closed-tomorrow-due-to-heavy-rain-4223096%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Political%20Violence%20Dents%20Bengal's%20Image%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Bengal's%20largest%20vernacular%20daily%20Anandabazar%20Patrika%20said%20in%20a%20front-page%20report%20that%20some%20of%20its%20reporters%20were%20huddled%20under%20a%20table%20to%20avoid%20splinters%20of%20crude%20bombs%20while%20covering%20the%20Panchayat%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20shivering%20with%20fear%2C%20wondering%20if%20hoodlums%20using%20those%20bombs%20would%20throw%20a%20few%20through%20the%20windows%20and%20the%20bombs%20would%20explode%20inside%20the%20room%20where%20we%20were%20hiding.%20It%20was%20nightmarish%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20reporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20violence%2C%20claim%20studies%2C%20has%20always%20been%20consistently%20high%20in%20Bengal.%20This%20time%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20violence%2C%20was%20an%20all-time%20high%20use%20of%20country-made%20firearms%20and%20crude%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20control%20of%20panchayats%2C%20or%20village%20councils%2C%20establishes%20political%20dominance%20at%20the%20local%20level%20and%20also%20helps%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20control%20the%20rural%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrude%20bombs%20were%20once%20used%20by%20Naxalites%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20and%20early%201970s%20during%20their%20pitched%20street%20battles%20with%20rival%20political%20parties%20and%20cops.%20The%20practice%20of%20making%20these%20bombs%20has%20continued%20for%20over%20six%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22qfkg9sk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqfkg9sk_bengal-election-violence_625x300_08_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20smaller%20versions%20of%20these%20crude%20bombs%20were%20manufactured%20across%20the%20state%20with%20a%20licence%20from%20the%20state%20government.%20When%20the%20licences%20were%20cancelled%2C%20a%20whole%20new%20small-scale%20industry%20mushroomed%20in%20the%20hinterland.%20For%20years%2C%20these%20bombs%20have%20been%20sold%20to%20members%20of%20political%20parties%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20darkness.%20It's%20a%20mini-industry%20worth%20crores.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20industry%20grows%20whenever%20there%20is%20an%20election%20in%20Bengal.%20Occasionally%2C%20these%20bombs%20are%20smuggled%20to%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%20and%20some%20other%20Indian%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBollywood%20director%20Anurag%20Kashyap%2C%20in%20his%20movie%20Gangs%20of%20Wasseypur%2C%20depicted%20the%20making%20of%20country-made%20bombs%20by%20criminals%20in%20Bihar%2C%20even%20from%20jails.%20Many%20black-and-white%20Bengali%20movies%2C%20like%20Aponjon%20directed%20by%20Tapan%20Sinha%2C%20had%20scenes%20of%20political%20activists%20singing%20Rabindrasangeet%20while%20tossing%20around%20crude%20bombs%20like%20cricket%20balls%20and%20then%20liberally%20using%20them%20against%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20in%20Kolkata%20told%20this%20reporter%20that%20these%20bombs%20are%20mostly%20used%20to%20create%20tensions%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%3B%20it%20works%20very%20well%20during%20elections.%20Voters%20avoid%20going%20to%20polling%20booths%20the%20moment%20they%20hear%20deafening%20blasts.%20Why%20risk%20injury%2C%20or%20worse%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22t605sleg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ft605sleg_bengal-panchayat-poll_625x300_14_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%20in%20Bengal%2C%20these%20very%20bombs%20and%20their%20liberal%20use%20by%20political%20parties%20caused%20devastation%20across%20the%20state%2C%20where%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20swept%20the%20Panchayat%20elections%20with%20a%20whopping%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-voltage%20violence%2C%20rampant%20booth%20capturing%2C%20and%20illegal%20stamping%20of%20ballot%20papers%20exposed%20the%20horrific%20reality%20of%20the%20election%20process%20that%20left%2053%20dead%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20central%20forces.%20This%20large-scale%20rigging%20desecrated%20the%20sanctity%20of%20elections%20to%2064%2C157%20seats%20in%20Gram%20Panchayats%2C%20Panchayat%20Samitis%2C%20and%20Zila%20Parishads%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20alarming%20is%20that%20the%20central%20forces%2C%20which%20must%20work%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20state%20police%2C%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20guard%20booths.%20The%20bloodiest%20panchayat%20poll%20in%20Bengal%20in%20this%20century%20was%20under%20the%20CPI(M)'s%20rule%20in%202003%20when%2076%20lives%20were%20lost.%20This%20time%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20cadres%20resorted%20to%20large-scale%20rigging%20by%20capturing%20booths%2C%20driving%20away%20polling%20agents%20of%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20stuffing%20ballot%20boxes%20with%20proxy%20votes%2C%20defiling%20the%20entire%20poll%20process.%20In%20many%20places%2C%20the%20presiding%20officers%20fled%20polling%20stations.%20Violence%20was%20reported%20from%20all%20over%20the%20state%3B%20the%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20Murshidabad%20districts%20witnessed%20intense%20violence%20and%20reported%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20said%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20of%20the%2061%2C636%20polling%20booths%20in%20the%20state%20were%20allegedly%20captured%20by%20Trinamool%20cadre%2C%20and%20huge%20numbers%20of%20proxy%20votes%20were%20cast.%20The%20bloodiest%20panchayat%20poll%20in%20Bengal%20in%20this%20century%20was%20under%20the%20CPI(M)'s%20watch%20in%202003%20when%2076%20lives%20were%20lost.%20In%202008%2C%20the%20number%20of%20dead%20was%2030%20and%20in%202013%20(two%20years%20after%20the%20Trinamool%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state)%20it%20was%2034.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20cognoscenti%20said%20infighting%20in%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20was%20also%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20the%20violence.%20The%20Trinamool's%20dominance%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20unchallenged%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20was%20facing%20resistance%20in%20various%20regions.%20In%20the%20panchayat%20polls%20in%202018%2C%20the%20party%20won%20about%20a%20third%20of%20the%20seats%20without%20any%20contest%3B%20this%20time%20around%2C%20it%20was%20about%2021%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%2C%20claimed%20experts%2C%20is%20caught%20in%20a%20debilitating%2C%20vicious%20cycle%20because%20there%20is%20very%20high%20unemployment%20and%20low%20activity%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%20and%20extreme%20corruption%20for%20political%20posts%20in%20the%20state.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20triggers%20extraction%20and%20corruption%20by%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20once%20violence%20ended%20and%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20the%20focus%20returned%20to%20the%20state%20and%20its%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%224dcndde8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4dcndde8_bengal-panchayat-poll-violence_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeasoned%20columnist%20and%20market%20tracker%20Mudar%20Patherya%2C%20in%20a%20brilliantly%20penned%20column%20titled%20The%20Best%20And%20Worst%20Of%20Panchayat%20Polls%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20worried%20after%20the%20polls%20as%20an%20urban%20resident.%20%26quot%3BThat%20Didi%20has%20swept%20the%20Bengal%20panchayat%20polls%20could%20be%20the%20best%20of%20news%20and%20the%20worst%20of%20news.%20Best%2C%20because%20it%20validates%20what%20she%20stands%20for.%20Worst%2C%20because%20it%20could%20convince%20her%20that%20nothing%20needs%20to%20change%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatherya%20wrote%20it%20was%20sad%20for%20him%20to%20think%20that%20there%20was%20no%20big%20Bengal%20picture%20beyond%20Modi%20%3Cem%3EHatao%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20unspoken%20vision%20statement%20of%20the%20Bengal%20government%20in%20four%20words%3A%20Win%20the%20next%20election.%20On%20what%20basis%20do%20we%20convince%20our%20children%20to%20stay%20behind%20after%20college%20and%20work%20from%20Calcutta%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDidi%20seeks%20to%20remove%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%20when%20she%20cannot%20evict%20hawker%20squatters%20from%20outside%20New%20Market%20or%20Chowringhee%3B%20or%20remove%20overhead%20cables%3B%20or%20remove%20vehicle%20strippers%20carving%20away%20one%20half%20of%20the%20Mullick%20Bazar%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Patherya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remembered%20a%20conversation%20between%20the%20Oberoi%20family%20and%20Trinamool%20brass%20for%20more%20hotels%2C%20to%20which%20the%20Oberois%20said%20they%20first%20wanted%20squatters%20removed%20from%20the%20pavements%20outside%20the%20hotel%20in%20Chowringhee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20columnist%20said%20he%20was%20distressed%20to%20see%20Bengal%20not%20figuring%20on%20the%20futuristic%20industrial%20and%20services%20radar%20of%20India%2C%20ostensibly%20because%20there%20were%20no%20investments%20worth%20mentioning%20related%20to%20renewable%20energy%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20or%20electric%20vehicles.%20%26quot%3BTen%20years%20from%20now%2C%20we%20will%20have%20the%20same%20Bengal%20companies%20manufacturing%20the%20same%20products%20with%2050%20per%20cent%20higher%20capacity%20and%2030%20per%20cent%20lower%20manpower%2C%20while%20the%20industrialists%20running%20those%20companies%20diversify%20their%20investments%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20I%20live%20to%20see%20the%20day%20when%20Bengal%20vies%20for%20a%20semiconductor%20chip%20unit%2C%20or%20Foxconn%20considers%20Bengal%20for%20an%20electronic%20manufacturing%20location%20or%20Bengal%20is%20selected%20as%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20manufacturing%20location.%20For%20a%20state%20that%20accounted%20for%2022%25%20of%20India's%20GDP%20in%20the%20mid-Sixties%2C%20we%20do%20not%20even%20qualify%20to%20play%20in%20the%20big%20tournament%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20the%20columnist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatherya%20said%20even%20the%20tourism%20sector%20was%20floundering%20despite%20some%20big-buck%20endorsements%20by%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan.%20%26quot%3BShah%20Rukh's%20endorsement%20of%20Bengal's%20tourism%20appeared%20mismatched%20(an%20actor%20who%20never%20spent%20even%20a%20fortnight%20holidaying%20in%20Bengal%20was%20championing%20the%20state's%20tourism%20to%20the%20world)%3B%20I%20doubt%20if%20Bengal%20even%20turns%20up%20at%20regional%20travel%20and%20tourism%20fairs%20where%20countries%20from%20the%20world%20(Saudi%20Arabia%20of%20all%20countries)%20pay%20top%20dollar%20to%20woo%20Indian%20tourists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatherya's%20words%20were%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20column%20some%20years%20ago%20by%20one%20Aditi%20Jain%2C%20whose%20father%20PC%20Jain%20was%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20McNally%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalcutta%20was%20a%20truly%20global%20city%20with%20a%20highly%20diversified%20demography.%20Commercial%20opportunities%20were%20considerable%20and%20so%20was%20the%20need%20for%20expertise.%20In%20Calcutta%2C%20there%20was%20serious%20money%20to%20be%20made.%20The%20tragedy%20is%20not%20that%20all%20of%20this%20was%20subsequently%20destroyed%3B%20the%20tragedy%20is%20that%20it%20can%20never%20be%20rebuilt%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20what%20happened%20to%20Calcutta%20and%20the%20entire%20industrial%20manufacturing%20of%20Bengal%20since%20the%201970s.%20Left%20Front%20governments%2C%20particularly%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Jyoti%20Basu%2C%20Bengal's%20erstwhile%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20cracked%20down%20on%20the%20industry%20and%20empowered%20unions%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20that%20factory%20after%20factory%20began%20to%20shut%20permanently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20narrated%20an%20incident%20that%20rattled%20her%20for%20life.%20%26quot%3BIn%201984%2C%20as%20a%20young%20project%20engineer%20responsible%20for%20a%20project%20site%20in%20Durgapur%2C%20where%20my%20employer%20was%20contracted%20to%20build%20a%20material%20handling%20plant%20for%20Hindustan%20Fertiliser%2C%20I%20was%20made%20to%20stand%20on%20an%20oil%20barrel%20for%20four%20hours%20in%20the%20mid-afternoon%20sun%2C%20with%20the%20labour%20unions%20shouting%20threatening%20slogans.%20The%20odd%20part%20was%20that%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20as%20to%20what%20I%20had%20done%20wrong%20or%20indeed%20what%20their%20demands%20were.%20Strikes%20and%20violence%20in%20those%20years%20were%20as%20common%20as%20reporting%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalcutta%2C%20upon%20which%20an%20empire%20had%20once%20been%20built%2C%20now%20lies%20reduced%20to%20just%20another%20fallen%20star.%20It%20has%20no%20credible%20prospect%20of%20returning%20to%20its%20former%20glory%2C%20at%20least%20in%20my%20lifetime.%20For%20me%20and%20an%20entire%20generation%20of%20Indians%20who%20remember%20that%20city%20for%20what%20it%20once%20was%2C%20that%20is%20a%20dreadful%20tragedy.%20Its%20demise%2C%20and%20indeed%20that%20of%20Bengal%2C%20is%20a%20clear%20example%20of%20the%20consequences%20of%20disrespect%20for%20wealth%20and%20those%20who%20create%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20wrote%20the%20column%20around%20the%20time%20the%20Trinamool%20swept%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20Things%20have%20turned%20worse%20since%3B%20trade%20unions%20have%20become%20tremendously%20powerful%20in%20Bengal%2C%20evident%20during%20the%20recent%20Panchayat%20polls.%20This%20is%20definitely%20not%20a%20good%20sign%20for%20the%20state%20and%20its%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shantanu%20Guha%20Ray%20is%20the%20Asia%20Editor%20of%20Central%20European%20News%2C%20UK)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689778560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fddsge928_bengal-violence_625x300_20_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-political-violence-dents-bengals-image-4223063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20week%2C%20Bengal's%20largest%20vernacular%20daily%20Anandabazar%20Patrika%20said%20in%20a%20front-page%20report%20that%20some%20of%20its%20reporters%20were%20huddled%20under%20a%20table%20to%20avoid%20splinters%20of%20crude%20bombs%20while%20covering%20the%20Panchayat%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-political-violence-dents-bengals-image-4223063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-political-violence-dents-bengals-image-4223063%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-political-violence-dents-bengals-image-4223063%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizens%2C%20Climate%20Action%20Groups%20Protest%20Against%20the%20Passage%20of%20Forest%20Conservation%20Amendment%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-