-taylor-matty-sophia-manganiello-10-celebrity-couples-who-broke-up-in-2023%2Fphotostory%2F101950807.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Researcher%E2%80%99s%20Bio%20Alternatives%20to%20Fertilisers%20%26%20Pesticides%20Help%2010000%20Farmers%20Avoid%20Losses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20spraying%20pesticides%20multiple%20times%20on%20her%20%3Cem%3Ekapas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cotton)%20crop%2C%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Anuja%20Deshmukh%20could%20not%20get%20a%20good%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSucking%20pests%20like%20mealy%20bugs%20and%20aphids%20attacked%20the%20cotton%20crop%20and%20would%20not%20die%20even%20after%20multiple%20spraying.%20For%20a%20four-month%20season%2C%20I%20had%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20up%20to%20seven%20times.%20But%2C%20I%20found%20that%20their%20resistance%20to%20chemical%20pesticides%20had%20also%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anuja%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2045-year-old%20farmer%20had%20tried%20different%20options%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20pests%20and%20failed.%20So%20when%20she%20heard%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F120349%2Finnovative-ways-pests-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebio-pesticides%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%20to%20chemical%20pesticides%20%E2%80%94%20around%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20was%20sceptical%20about%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20could%20not%20believe%20that%20using%20bio-pesticides%20would%20be%20of%20any%20help.%20But%20since%20this%20was%20our%20last%20resort%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20giving%20it%20a%20try.%20Initially%2C%20I%20sprayed%20only%2020%20percent%20of%20my%20crop%20with%20it%2C%20and%20I%20got%20good%20results%20in%20flowering%20and%20my%20yield%20increased%20up%20to%2030%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigur