%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangita%20says%20that%20bio%20alternatives%20save%20one-third%20costs%20of%20farmers%20as%20compared%20to%20chemical%20fertilisers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20driven%20by%20her%20motivation%2C%20Sangita%20started%20studying%20biological%20pest%20control%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CPests%20like%20white%20grub%20eat%20the%20root%20of%20crops%20and%20pose%20a%20big%20problem%20for%20farmers%20in%20fields.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20usage%20of%20bio-pesticides.%20I%20started%20studying%20parasite%20predators%20and%20found%20that%20there%20are%20some%20microorganisms%20like%20Trichoderma%20harzianum%20which%20control%20pest%20attack%20by%20destroying%20their%20eggs%20and%20larvae%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20she%20found%20bio%20alternatives%20to%20control%20pests%20like%20white%20grubs%2C%20mealybugs%2C%20mites%2C%20aphids%2C%20jassids%2C%20and%20more.%20And%20in%201998%2C%20her%20experiments%20resulted%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vidarbhabiotechlab.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Vidarbha%20Biotech%20Ltd%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20sells%2016%20kinds%20of%20bio-pesticides%2C%20bio-fungicides%2C%20and%20bio-fertilisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20these%20products%20using%20microorganisms%20like%20fungi%2C%20bacteria%20and%20viruses%20which%20cannot%20be%20seen%20with%20the%20naked%20eye%20but%20are%20useful%20for%20crops.%20We%20term%20them%20as%20friends%20of%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESold%20in%20liquid%20as%20well%20as%20powder%20form%2C%20these%20products%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%20250%20and%20Rs%20400.%20The%20products%20have%20certification%20from%20the%20Central%20Insecticide%20Board%2C%20Faridabad.%20Other%20than%20conventional%20farming%2C%20these%20bio-pesticides%20a