9776546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2FNaganah-Anishas-groundskeeper-sprays-a-completely-organic-pesticide-on-the-crops.-1-1660831020.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324349%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saddened%20by%20increasing%20farmer%20suicides%2C%20agriculture%20entomologist%20Sangita%20Sawalakhe%20innovated%20bio%20alternatives%20to%20chemical%20pesticides%20and%20fertilisers.%20She%20started%20Vidarbha%20Biotech%20Ltd%20and%20has%20helped%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Punjab%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324349%2Fmaharashtra-agriculture-entomologist-sangita-sawalakhe-vidarbha-biotech-biopesticides-biofertilisers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Next%20Pandemic%20Will%20Come%2C%20It's%20Only%20A%20Matter%20Of%20Time%3A%20World%20Bank%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20head%20of%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20Ajay%20Banga%2C%20has%20warned%20that%20it's%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20until%20the%20world%20witnesses%20another%20pandemic%20like%20Covid-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20Skill%20India%20Mission%20centre%20in%20New%20Delhi's%20Dwarka%20today%2C%20Mr%20Banga%20said%20that%20the%20pandemic%20caused%20extreme%20learning%20losses%2C%20which%20is%20posing%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20generation%20that%20went%20for%20schooling%20during%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Bank%2C%20in%20a%202021%20report%2C%20had%20said%20that%20learning%20losses%20from%20Covid-19%20could%20cost%20this%20generation%20of%20students%20close%20to%20%2417%20trillion%20in%20lifetime%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'We%20have%20to%20fix%20what%20happened%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20we%20learn%20for%20the%20next%20pandemic.%20Because%20the%20next%20pandemic%20will%20come%2C%20it's%20only%20a%20question%20of%20how%20long%20before%20it%20comes%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Banga%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20Indian-Origin%20World%20Bank%20chief%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banga%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20the%20World%20Bank%20President%20last%20month%2C%20also%20stressed%20on%20climate%20finance%20during%20his%20India%20visit.%20He%20said%20there's%20a%20requirement%20of%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20a%20year%20to%20be%20invested%20in%20renewable%20energy%20ecosystem%20across%20the%20world%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'You%20cannot%20get%20that%20kind%20of%20money%20from%20governments%2C%20%C2%A0philanthropists%20or%20multilateral%20banks%20alone%2C%20you%20have%20to%20get%20the%20private%20sector%20along%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Banga%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20world%20is%20facing%20many%20crises%2C%20such%20as%20'climate%20issues%2C%20issues%20with%20fragility%2C%20conflict%2C%20pandemic%2C%20future%20healthcare%20needs%2C%20poverty%2C%20and%20creating%20jobs'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Bank%20head%20said%20that%20the%20world%20should%20use%20the%20money%20it%20already%20has%20in%20the%20best%20way%20possible%2C%20and%20then%20come%20back%20to%20the%20richer%20countries%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20your%20ambition%20for%20the%20future%20and%20how%20much%20money%20are%20you%20willing%20to%20put%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20pandemic's%20global%20impact%2C%20Mr.%20Banga%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20had%20a%20year%20or%20two%20of%20challenges%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20but%20you've%20come%20out%20of%20it%20pretty%20strong%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20his%20optimism%20for%20the%20Indian%20economy%20is%20based%20on%20the%20country's%20investment%20in%20digital%20and%20physical%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Bank%20chief%20was%20in%20India%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20Finance%20Ministers%20and%20Central%20Bank%20Governors%20meet%20that%20concluded%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689776400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fh102h1ro_ajay-bangag20world-bank_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnext-pandemic-will-come-only-a-question-of-when-world-bank-chief-4222887%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20head%20of%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20Ajay%20Banga%2C%20has%20warned%20that%20it's%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20until%20the%20world%20witnesses%20another%20pandemic%20like%20Covid-19.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnext-pandemic-will-come-only-a-question-of-when-world-bank-chief-4222887%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnext-pandemic-will-come-only-a-question-of-when-world-bank-chief-4222887%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnext-pandemic-will-come-only-a-question-of-when-world-bank-chief-4222887%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20Prigozhin%20says%20his%20mercenaries%20will%20not%20fight%20in%20Ukraine%20for%20now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689776165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101959297%2Cimgsize-522274.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussias-prigozhin-says-his-mercenaries-will-not-fight-in-ukraine-for-now%2Farticleshow%2F101959124.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101959124.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERussian%20mercenary%20boss%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%20was%20shown%20in%20a%20video%20welcoming%20his%20Wagner%20figh