by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20INDIA%20claims%20it%20wants%20to%20reclaim%20lost%20democracy%20and%20constitutionalism%20and%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20leads%20the%20NDA%2C%20has%20launched%20a%20barrage%20of%20accusations%20against%20the%20opposition%2C%20painting%20them%20as%20corrupt%2C%20dynasts%20and%20opportunists.%20In%20the%20war%20of%20words%2C%20%C2%A0what%20is%20certain%20is%20that%20the%20battle%20for%202024%20is%20no%20longer%20one-sided%20and%20that%20Modi%20can't%20claim%20a%20walkover%20as%20he%20had%20in%20the%20two%20previous%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20several%20sceptics%2C%20even%20in%20the%20Left-liberal%20fold%2C%20who%20were%20not%20sure%20about%20opposition%20leaders%20ever%20coming%20together%20under%20the%20same%20umbrella%2C%20with%20big%20egos%20clashing%2C%20the%20difference%20of%20ideologies%20and%20political%20opportunism.%20But%20the%20smoothness%20with%20which%20they%20came%20together%20and%20created%20INDIA%2C%20the%20acronym%20representing%20a%20new%20political%20force%20to%20take%20Modi%20head-on%2C%20has%20surprised%20many.%20A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20even%20leaders%20in%20the%20anti-Modi%20camp%20were%20unsure%20of%20any%20such%20alliance%20working%20out%2C%20given%20the%20political%20disparateness.%20There%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20hopelessness%20and%20despondency%20despite%20their%20common%20view%20that%20unless%20they%20joined%20forces%2C%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20be%20defeated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20myth%20has%20been%20shattered.%20Twenty-six%20parties%20have%20promised%20to%20fight%20together.%20The%20credit%20should%20be%20given%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20It%20wouldn't%20have%20come%20to%20pass%20if%20he%20had%20not%20created%20the%20'new%20normal'%20in%20which%20he%20breached%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20democracy%2C%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20for%20all%20and%20that%20central%20agencies%20are%20free%20from%20the%20clutches%20of%20political%20masters.%20The%20relentless%20targeting%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20by%20these%20agencies%2C%20led%20by%20bureaucrats%20who%20once%20swore%20by%20the%20Constitution%20but%20are%20now%20drunk%20on%20loyalty%20to%20a%20leader%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20opposition%20parties%20are%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20fight%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20never%20witnessed%20such%20brazen%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20before.%20Today%2C%20among%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20cases%20involving%20political%20leaders%20and%20parties%2C%2095%25%20are%20against%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20only%205%25%20are%20against%20those%20who%20are%20either%20with%20the%20BJP%20or%20support%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre.%20Opposition%20leaders%20are%20regularly%20raided%2C%20their%20properties%20are%20confiscated%20and%20attached%20by%20ED%20officials%2C%20and%20they%20are%20sent%20to%20jail%2C%20where%20they%20languish%20for%20months%20and%20years%20without%20any%20hope%20of%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20assault%20on%20their%20constitutionally%20granted%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%26quot%3B%20had%20them%20facing%20an%20existential%20crisis%20-%20either%20fight%20to%20survive%20or%20surrender%20to%20servitude.%20The%20onslaught%20is%20multifaceted.%20Not%20only%20central%20agencies%20but%20also%20Governors%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governors%20appointed%20by%20the%20Centre%20have%20made%20life%20hell%20for%20governments%20ruled%20by%20the%20opposition.%20The%20mainstream%20media%20has%20been%20discrediting%20them%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20portraying%20them%20as%20anti-India%2C%20corrupt%20and%20opportunistic.%20Every%20effort%20is%20made%20to%20choke%20them%20financially.%20The%20situation%20has%20reached%20a%20point%20that%20they%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20even%20speak%20in%20parliament.%20If%20they%20speak%2C%20then%20their%20speech%20is%20either%20expunged%20or%20they%20are%20removed%20from%20parliament.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20an%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20big%20surprise%20if%20the%20opposition%20had%20not%20come%20together.%20The%20ruling%20dispensation%20had%20probably%20not%20imagined%20this%20would%20happen%20quite%20so%20smoothly%2C%20and%20so%20fast.%20The%20Prime%20Minister's%20two%20speeches%2C%20on%20a%20day%20the%20opposition%20had%20gathered%20to%20announce%20their%20togetherness%2C%20is%20proof%20that%20he%20is%20either%20rattled%20or%20has%20been%20caught%20off%20guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20a%20good%20speaker.%20He%20never%20minces%20his%20words%20while%20attacking%20his%20opponents%2C%20but%20the%20kind%20of%20speech%20he%20gave%2C%20his%20choice%20of%20words%20to%20attack%20the%20opposition%20and%20his%20body%20language%20betrayed%20nervousness%20in%20the%20ruling%20camp.%20The%20BJP%20should%20know%20more%20than%20any%20other%20party%20that%20whenever%20the%20opposition%20has%20united%2C%20however%20fragmented%20or%20marginal%2C%20it%20has%20hurt%20the%20party%20in%20power.%20The%20examples%20are%20plenty%20in%201967%2C%201977%20and%201989.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20when%20the%20Congress%20used%20to%20walk%20like%20a%20colossus%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20The%20opposition%20parties%20were%20too%20small%20to%20confront%20the%20Congress%20but%20collectively%2C%20they%20inflicted%20major%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%20argue%20that%202024%20is%20different.%20But%20such%20arguments%20were%20also%20trotted%20out%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%201967%2C%201977%20and%201989%2C%20and%20we%20all%20know%20how%20that%20ended.%20Today%2C%20defying%20perception%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20emerged%20far%20stronger%20than%20ever%20before.%20Today%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20governments%20in%2011%20states%2C%20which%20was%20never%20the%20case%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20often%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20too%20weak%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20Critics%20forget%20that%20on%20earlier%20occasions%2C%20there%20was%20no%20party%20in%20the%20opposition%20that%20could%20have%20claimed%20a%20national%20footprint%20and%20governments%20in%20states.%20The%20BJP%20(Jana%20Sangh)%2C%20the%20Left%20and%20socialists%20had%20a%20national%20vision%20but%20no%20national%20presence.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20now%20on%20pole%20position%2C%20formed%20the%20first%20government%20on%20its%20own%20on%204%20March%201990%20in%20Rajasthan.%20It%20was%20led%20by%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%20Today%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20governments%20in%20four%20states%2C%20and%20in%20two%20it%20is%20a%20coalition%20partner.%20The%20party%20has%20won%2012%20crore%20votes%20nationally.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20now%20in%20the%20government%2C%20had%20seven%20crore%20votes%20in%202009.%20Modi%20is%20too%20astute%20a%20politician%20not%20to%20know%20this%20political%20reality.%20So%2C%20his%20desperation%20is%20understandable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cobbling%20of%2037%20parties%20overnight%20by%20the%20BJP%20bears%20testimony%20to%20my%20argument%20that%20Modi%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20danger%20of%20the%20BJP%20underestimating%20the%20opposition%20meet.%20He%20is%20the%20man%20who%20declared%20in%20parliament%20that%20he%20alone%20is%20enough%20to%20vanquish%20the%20collective%20might%20of%20opposition%20leaders.%20He%20knows%20that%20in%20politics%2C%20perception%20is%20very%20important.%20Hence%2C%20the%20effort%20to%20showcase%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20support%20of%20more%20political%20parties%20than%20the%20opposition.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20opposition%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20intimidated%20by%20numbers.%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20done%20its%20homework%20better.%20The%20name%20given%20to%20the%20opposition%20front%20-%20INDIA%20-%20stands%20as%20a%20testament.%20It%20is%20no%20ordinary%20name.%20It%20tries%20to%20tackle%20every%20accusation%20the%20BJP%20has%20flung%20at%20them%20since%202014.%20The%20name%20is%20strategic%2C%20political%20and%20also%20ideological.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20stands%20for%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance.%20First%2C%20let's%20look%20at%20the%20word%20INDIA.%20Can%20the%20BJP%20now%20abuse%20the%20word%20INDIA%20like%20it%20would%20have%20done%20with%20UPA%3F%20Can%20it%20say%20INDIA%20is%20anti-India%20or%20INDIA%20is%20pro-Pakistan%3F%20It%20can't.%20It%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20reclaim%20the%20word%20India%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20under%20Modi%20has%20snatched%20from%20them.%20Modi%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20has%20claimed%20to%20be%20synonymous%20with%20India.%20He%20is%20India%20and%20any%20attack%20on%20him%20has%20been%20described%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20India.%20The%20opposition%20has%20tried%20to%20counter%20that%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20been%20dubbed%20anti-national%20ever%20so%20often.%20The%20BJP%20has%20become%20the%20harbinger%20of%20nationalism%2C%20and%20those%20who%20oppose%20the%20party%20are%20termed%20anti-national.%20So%20the%20%26quot%3BNational%26quot%3B%20in%20INDIA%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20they%20are%20also%20nationalistic%2C%20but%20not%20like%20the%20BJP%20or%20RSS%20-%20their%20nationalism%20is%20inclusive.%20That%20they%20do%20not%20discriminate%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20and%20caste.%20That%20their%20nationalism%20has%20a%20place%20for%20every%20citizen%3B%20and%20that%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Christians%2C%20and%20other%20minorities%20should%20not%20worry%20about%20their%20identities.%20They%20are%20at%20par%20with%20Hindus%20and%20will%20be%20treated%20as%20such%2C%20unlike%20the%20BJP%20claiming%20to%20take%20everyone%20along%2C%20but%20favouring%20Hindus%20over%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%2C%20Modi%20has%20also%20hijacked%20the%20word%20Development.%20He%20does%20not%20miss%20any%20opportunity%20to%20boast%20about%20India%20growing%20economically%20and%20claim%20that%20on%20his%20watch%20India%20became%20the%20fastest%20growing%20economy%20and%20fifth%20largest%20in%20size.%20To%20underline%20its%20development%20narrative%2C%20the%20BJP%20always%20talks%20about%20double%20engine%20ki%20sarkar%20(a%20government%20with%20a%20double%20engine).%20The%20opposition's%20use%20of%20the%20word%20Developmental%20is%20an%20answer%20to%20that%20claim%2C%20an%20attempt%20to%20reclaim%20the%20growth%20turf%20and%20tell%20the%20voter%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20launched%20OG%20reforms%20to%20foster%20economic%20growth%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20INDIA%20is%20also%20an%20argument%20to%20project%20the%20opposition%20front%20as%20an%20ideological%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Hindutva.%20INDIA%20is%20unity%20in%20diversity%2C%20it%20is%20multicultural%2C%20with%20space%20for%20all%20faiths%2C%20where%20everyone%20is%20treated%20equally%2C%20in%20which%20no%20identity%20-%20%C2%A0national%20or%20sub-national%2C%20regional%20or%20sub-regional%2C%20linguistic%20or%20tribal%20-%20is%20discriminated%20against.%20For%20them%20the%20constitution%20is%20religion%20instead%20of%20religion%20being%20the%20guiding%20principle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%3B%20INDIA%20must%20now%20evolve%20and%20emerge%20as%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP.%20I%20am%20sure%2C%20with%20%C2%A0Modi's%20appetite%20for%20politics%20and%20power%2C%20his%20tenacity%2C%20his%20resilience%2C%20flexibility%20and%20ideological%20commitment%2C%20the%20road%20ahead%20won't%20be%20a%20smooth%20one%20for%20the%20opposition%20INDIA.%20Any%20attack%20on%20them%20will%20be%20more%20severe%20and%20direct%20than%20ever%20before.%20Modi's%20speech%20was%20just%20a%20preview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20The