rn%20liberal%20polity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20situation%20unfolding%20in%20Manipur%20begs%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20there%20really%20is%20a%20civil%20society%20%E2%80%93%20as%20opposed%20to%20politicians%20and%20members%20of%20militant%20organisations%20%E2%80%93%20left%20outside%20the%20ecology%20of%20violence%20and%20antagonism%2C%20who%20can%20decisively%20intervene%20in%20the%20conflagration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22942%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM.png%20942w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM-300x162.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-653506%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22510%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20from%20a%20video%20purportedly%20showing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20on%20the%20night%20of%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20an%20observer%20from%20afar%20%E2%80%93%20and%20with%20credible%20information%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20make%20its%20way%20out%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20take%20a%20well-informed%20stance%20on%20it.%20Moreover%2C%20my%20endeavour%20here%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20comprehensive%20answers%2C%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%20to%20analyse%20the%20elite%20condescension%20and%20na%C3%AFvet%C3%A9%20involved%20in%20prescribing%20solutions%20for%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20the%20national%20media%20discourse%20about%20Manipur%20attributes%20the%20conflict%20to%20pre-modern%20communal%2Ftribal%20allegiances%20of%20the%20people%20there.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20solution%20is%20almost%20always%20a%20call%20to%20summon%20the%20imaginary%20civil%20society%20and%20double%20down%20on%20modernist%20values%2C%20including%20appeals%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20to%20see%20themselves%20as%20citizens%20of%20a%20republic%2C%20rather%20than%20as%20subjects%20of%20subnational%20community%20identities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20point%20is%3A%20After%20more%20than%2070%20years%20of%20implementing%20prescriptions%20hinged%20on%20modern%20political%20principles%2C%20it%20is%20high%20time%20to%20question%20these%20normative%20notions%20and%20investigate%20whether%20the%20so-called%20solution%20has%20itself%20become%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-kashmir-disempowerment-northeast%5C%22%3EEchoes%20of%20Kashmiri%20Disempowerment%20Are%20Being%20Felt%20in%20the%20Northeast%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20divide%20so%20complete%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20communal%20violence%20of%20this%20scale%20and%20magnitude%20has%20been%20unprecedented%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20seems%20that%20unlike%20before%2C%20this%20violence%20is%20more%20decentralised%2C%20pervasive%20and%20people-to-people%2C%20rather%20than%20one%20driven%20by%20exclusive%20or%20fringe%20groups%20of%20militants%20fighting%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it%20is%20now%20mostly%20the%20civilian%20public%20who%20constitute%20this%20ecology%20of%20intense%20antagonism%20and%20bloodshed%2C%20and%20who%20have%20taken%20up%20arms%2C%20either%20as%20the%20aggressor%20or%20the%20resistor.%20The%20pervasive%20nature%20of%20this%20current%20instance%20of%20communal%20violence%20leaves%20no%20space%20for%20an%20apolitical%2C%20modern%2C%20and%20liberal%20%E2%80%98silent%20majority%E2%80%99%20to%20exist%20outside%20of%20its%20ecology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20saying%20this%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20imply%20that%20there%20is%20absolutely%20no%20one%20outside%20the%20ecology%20of%20violence.%20My%20argument%20is%20also%20not%20that%20all%20the%20men%20and%20women%20in%20Manipur%20have%20armed%20themselves%20and%20are%20on%20the%20streets%20attacking%20or%20resisting.%20Rather%2C%20my%20argument%20is%20that%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20there%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20discernible%20group%20capable%20of%20acting%20as%20legitimate%20political%20agents%20to%20effect%20a%20third-party%20intervention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20complete%20failure%20of%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20state%20to%20legitimately%20intervene%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this%20is%20telling.%20The%20state%20government%20led%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Biren%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Meitei%20himself%20%E2%80%93%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-manipur-cm-anti-kuki-separate-state-wilson-lalam-hangshing-karan-thapar%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20openly%20siding%20with%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20aiding%20the%20Kuki%20minority%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20alienation%2C%20both%20in%20the%20violent%20culmination%20and%20in%20the%20antagonistic%20build-up%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20seems%20like%20the%20state%20administration%20and%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20were%20themselves%20split%20on%20communal%20lines.%20This%20episode%20is%20also%20unprecedented%20as%20the%20violence%20is%20being%20fuelled%20by%20advanced%20weaponry%20and%20ammunition%20that%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-looted-weaponry-yet-to-return-to-police-armouries-cm-appeals-afresh-for-surrender%5C%22%3Estolen%20or%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20police%20stations%20and%20armouries%20of%20the%20state%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-300x221.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3-1024x754.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGun%20drop%20box%20placed%20in%20Imphal%20Manipur.%20Authorities%20are%20asking%20people%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20snatched%20and%20looted%20weapons.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20it%20is%20so-called%20volunteers%20from%20among%20the%20communities%20themselves%2C%20who%20have%20been%20guarding%20their%20own%20villages%20or%20attacking%20others.%20There%20are%20several%20harrowing%20testimonies%20from%20victims%20in%20the%20media%20about%20how%20the%20violence%20is%20being%20perpetrated%20by%20common%20people%20(neighbours%20in%20some%20cases)%20rather%20than%20any%20armed%20militant%20organisations.%20The%20Meira%20Paibis%20(%E2%80%98women%20torchbearers%E2%80%99)%2C%20a%20well-known%20grassroots%2C%20and%20predominantly%20Meitei%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20organisation%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fwomen-activists-accompany-armed-rioters-and-blocking-routes-and-interfering-in-operations-says-army%2Farticle67013135.ece%5C%22%3Eblocking%20the%20central%20forces%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20reaching%20violence-hit%20areas%20on%20many%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20all-pervasive%20nature%20of%20the%20antagonism%20is%20also%20evident%20in%20the%20way%20religion%20has%20come%20to%20be%20imbricated%20in%20it.%20Unlike%20before%2C%20the%20primarily%20ethnic%20conflagrations%20have%20also%20attained%20a%20strong%20anti-Christian%20hue%2C%20making%20the%20antagonism%20deep%20on%20several%20levels%20and%20not%20just%20on%20perceived%20ethnic%20lines.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20antagonism%20is%20totally%20formless.%20There%20are%20civilian%20groups%20which%20call%20themselves%20cultural%20organisations%2C%20like%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%2C%20who%20have%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20and%20fanning%20the%20age-old%20distrust%20between%20the%20communities%20and%20bringing%20it%20to%20a%20head.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20will%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20while%20the%20ecology%20of%20violence%20and%20antagonism%20is%20grassroots%20and%20decentralised%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20method%20to%20it%2C%20and%20there%20are%20self-proclaimed%20cultural%20organisations%20playing%20a%20vanguard%20role.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20panellist%20on%20a%20TV%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DakXc18hm4vU%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ediscussion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20pointed%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20divide%20is%20so%20complete!%E2%80%9D%20Moreover%2C%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20left%20in%20the%20valleys%20and%20any%20Meitei%20left%20in%20the%20hills.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20issue%20is%20being%20framed%20on%20national%20TV%20%E2%80%93%20that%20a%20few%20militant%20organisations%2C%20detached%20from%20the%20larger%20society%20are%20fighting%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20seems%20to%20be%20false%20and%20misleading.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20government%20and%20the%20public%20sphere%20are%20so%20divided%20on%20ethnic%20lines%2C%20there%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20space%20for%20a%20civil%20society%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIs%20modernist%20rhetoric%20aiding%20majoritarianism%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBimol%20Akoijam%2C%20a%20sociologist%20at%20JNU%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWH7Sk9KOD84%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eobjected%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20insisted%20that%20the%20only%20category%20applicable%20to%20the%20Kukis%20or%20anyone%20else%20in%20Manipur%20should%20be%20that%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccitizen%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20should%20be%20noted%20here%20that%20as%20far%20as%20the%20state%20is%20concerned%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20category%20that%20recognises%20a%20tribe%20as%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20grant%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20prioritises%20demographically%20smaller%20communities%2C%20whereas%20the%20category%20of%20%E2%80%98citizen%E2%80%99%20foregrounds%20the%20individual%2C%20and%20not%20their%20community%2C%20as%20the%20rights-bearing%20subject.%20Throughout%20the%20world%2C%20and%20in%20Indian%20constitutional%20practice%2C%20individual%20and%20group%20rights%20can%20and%20do%20coexist.%20Doing%20away%20with%20the%20distinctive%20category%20of%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%20or%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(used%20interchangeably%20in%20this%20context)%20and%20imposing%20a%20homogenising%20term%20like%20%E2%80%98citizen%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20only%20bearer%20of%20rights%20is%20violent%20on%20two%20primary%20counts%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20it%20falsely%20assumes%20that%20every%20individual%20is%20equally%20privileged%20by%20the%20state%20and%20its%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20which%20negates%20the%20history%20and%20reality%20of%20community-based%20discrimination.%20Two%2C%20it%20serves%20to%20delegitimise%20affirmative%20provisions%20for%20social%20groups%20that%20are%20aimed%20at%20addressing%20historical%20inequalities%20and%20protecting%20minority%20cultures%20from%20being%20obscured%20by%20the%20majority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20sense%2C%20insistence%20upon%20using%20%E2%80%98citizen%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20more%20broadly%2C%20the%20rhetoric%20of%20modernism%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20legitimise%20a%20majoritarian%20project%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20anything%2C%20a%20just%20solution%20to%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20will%20have%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20prescriptions%20of%20normative%20modernist%20politics.%20Such%20a%20stance%20will%20have%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20social%20reality%20that%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20are%20still%20circumscribed%20and%20defined%20by%20their%20community%20locations%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEspecially%20in%20situations%20like%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20the%20state%20is%20apparently%20part%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20project%2C%20it%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20people%20hark%20back%20to%20their%20traditional%20community%20affiliations%20as%20a%20means%20of%20survival%20and%20resistance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBipin%20Sebastian%20is%20a%20PhD%20student%20in%20the%20programme%20of%20Rhetoric%20and%20Public%20Culture%20at%20Northwestern%20University%2C%20Evanston%2C%20Illinois.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689764401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11194911%2FF0ubs4CWcAEONzp.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-modernist-prescriptions-majoritarian-project%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One-stop%20solutions%20like%20involving%20civil%20society%20and%20using%20modernist%20rhetoric%20have%20been%20offered%20as%20ways%20to%20end%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20between%20Kukis%20and%20Meiteis.%20But%20it%20is%20time%20to%20ask%20if%20the%20proposed%20solution%20has%20become%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-modernist-prescriptions-majoritarian-project%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Egypt%3A%20Researcher%20Patrick%20Zaki%20Sentenced%20to%20Three%20Years%20in%20Jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19160856%2Fpatrick-zaki.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0court%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fegypt%2Ft-18332328%5C%22%3EEgypt%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20sentenced%20rights%20researcher%20Patrick%20Zaki%20to%20three%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20%E2%80%9Cspreading%20false%20news%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20Egyptian%20Initiative%20for%20Personal%20Rights%20(EIPR)%2C%20the%20human%20rights%20organisation%20where%20Zaki%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20been%20arrested%20now%20and%20is%20being%20transferred%20to%20jail