.R.%20Gavai%2C%20A.S.%20Bopanna%2C%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said%20today%20that%20this%20order%20was%20%E2%80%9Cperverse%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20pains%20to%20say%20that%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20learned%20judge%20makes%20an%20interesting%20reading%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-teesta-setalvad-gujarat-high-court-grant-regular-bail-233094%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cone%20hand%2C%20the%20learned%20judge%20has%20spent%20pages%20to%20observe%20as%20to%20how%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20rather%20nor%20permissible%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20bail%20to%20consider%20whether%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20is%20made%20out%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20then%20criticised%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20since%20Setalvad%20had%20not%20challenged%20the%20FIR%20against%20her%2C%20she%20could%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20say%20whether%20the%20case%20against%20her%20was%20made%20out%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20observation%20of%20the%20learned%20judge%20are%20to%20be%20accepted%2C%20no%20application%20for%20bail%20can%20be%20accepted%20unless%20the%20accused%20files%20an%20application%20for%20quashing%20the%20proceedings%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20highlighted%20that%20the%20three%20considerations%20during%20the%20granting%20of%20bail%20are%20what%20the%20case%20looks%20like%2C%20prima%20facie%20case%2C%20what%20possibility%20of%20the%20accused%20tampering%20with%20evidence%20or%20influencing%20the%20witness%20exists%20and%20the%20chance%20of%20the%20accused%20fleeing%20from%20justice%2C%20along%20with%20the%20gravity%20of%20her%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20say%20the%20least%2C%20the%20findings%20are%20totally%20perverse.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20learned%20judge%20goes%20on%20to%20discuss%20the%20statements%20of%20some%20witnesses%20and%20finds%20that%20prima%20facie%20case%20is%20made%20out.%20The%20findings%20are%20totally%20contradictory%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20in%20a%20late%20night%20sitting%20on%20July%201%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20granted%20interim%20relief%20to%20Setalvad%2C%20with%20Justice%20B.R.%20Gavai%20asking%2C%20%E2%80%9CWill%20the%20skies%20fall%20if%20interim%20protection%20is%20granted%20for%20some%20days%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-extends-teesta-setalvad-interim-bail-july-19%5C%22%3Eextended%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20interim%20bail%20until%20July%2019%2C%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Setalvad%20was%20arrested%20from%20her%20Mumbai%20home%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20Anti-Terror%20Squad%20soon%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20judgment%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EZakia%20Jafri%3C%2Fem%3E%20case.%20Jafri%20and%20Setalvad%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20had%20centred%20around%20the%20closure%20report%20of%20the%20special%20investigation%20team%20which%20probed%20the%20murder%20of%20Jafri%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Ehsan%2C%20in%20the%202002%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SC%20not%20only%20disposed%20the%20appeal%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20Setalvad%20was%20among%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20who%20had%20kept%20the%20pot%20boiling%E2%80%9D%20with%20an%20%E2%80%9Culterior%20motive%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20past%2016%20years.%20It%20added%20that%20she%20should%20be%20in%20the%20dock%20and%20be%20%E2%80%9Cproceeded%20with%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetalvad%20spent%20around%2070%20days%20in%20jail.%20Former%20SC%20judge%20Justice%20Ma