gement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-prepares-for-naval-drills-with-russia-in-sign-of-continuing-support-amid-ukraine-conflict%2Farticleshow%2F101937306.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-prepares-for-naval-drills-with-russia-in-sign-of-continuing-support-amid-ukraine-conflict%2Famp_articleshow%2F101937306.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-prepares-for-naval-drills-with-russia-in-sign-of-continuing-support-amid-ukraine-conflict%2Famp_articleshow%2F101937306.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yet%20Again%2C%20No%20Joint%20Statement%20After%20G20%20Finance%20Ministers%20Meeting%20Due%20to%20Ukraine%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19143244%2FF1THyNVWcAAkEk1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20expected%2C%20the%20G20%20finance%20ministers%20concluded%20their%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20without%20any%20joint%20statement%20due%20to%20their%20continuing%20differences%20over%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20two-day%20meeting%20of%20finance%20ministers%20and%20central%20bank%20governors%20of%20G-20%20members%20wrapped%20up%20without%20a%20final%20communique%2C%20but%20India%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g20.org%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fgtwenty%2Fgtwenty_new%2Fdocument%2F3rd_G20_FMCBG_Outcome_Document_and_Chair%2527s_Summary.pdf%5C%22%3Echair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20document%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g20.org%2Fen%2Fmedia-resources%2Fdocuments%2Fdoc-outcomes%2F%5C%22%3Elast%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20joint%20statement%20was%20issued%20was%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%2C%20Indonesia%20in%20November%202022.%20India%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20issued%20nine%20chair%E2%80%99s%20summaries%20after%20G20%20meetings%20in%20lieu%20of%20any%20common%20communique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Indian%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20there%20was%20no%20consensus%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Findia-g20-russia-ukraine-sitharaman-gandhinagar-2102e0fad5017a230718d59619d615a3%5C%22%3Ebecause%20we%20still%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20common%20language%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20previous%20chair%E2%80%99s%20summaries%2C%20there%20were%20two%20written%20disclaimers.%20One%20was%20China%20stating%20that%20the%20G20%20meeting%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20the%20right%20forum%20to%20discuss%20geo-political%20issues%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0The%20second%20was%20Russia%20disassociating%20from%20three%20paragraphs%20in%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20paragraph%20that%20Russia%20objected%20to%20had%20deplored%20the%20%E2%80%9CRussian%20aggression%20in%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstrongest%20terms%E2%80%9D%20and%20also%20demanded%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20and%20unconditional%20withdrawal%E2%80%9D%20of%20Russian%20troops%20from%20Ukrainian%20territory.%20The%20consecutive%20paragraph%20called%20for%20upholding%20the%20UN%20charter%2C%20peaceful%20resolution%20as%20well%20as%2C%20the%20line%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctoday%E2%80%99s%20era%20must%20not%20be%20of%20war%E2%80%9D.%20This%20was%20the%20message%20that%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20told%20the%20Russian%20president%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20since%20been%20praised%20and%20inserted%20by%20the%20West%20in%20several%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20finance%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20language%20describing%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20had%20been%20drawn%20directly%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20G20%20leaders%20summit%20declaration%20in%20Indonesia.%20Stating%20the%20ministers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20mandate%20to%20change%20that%2C%20she%20added%20that%20this%20was%20an%20issue%20that%20the%20leaders%20will%20have%20to%20decide%20when%20they%20meet%20in%20the%20Indian%20capital%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fifth%20paragraph%20in%20the%20chair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20was%20about%20how%20to%20combat%20food%20insecurity%2C%20with%20G20%20ministers%20noting%20that%20prices%20have%20fallen%20but%20that%20there%20remained%20high%20potential%20for%20volatility%20in%20food%20and%20energy%20markets.%20It%20also%20welcomed%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20report%20on%20Macroeconomic%20Impacts%20of%20Food%20and%20Energy%20Insecurity%20and%20their%20Implications%20for%20the%20Global%20Economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post-meeting%20press%20conference%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fg20-meeting-india-end-without-communique-ukraine-war-divides-bloc-2023-07-18%2F%5C%22%3Efood%20insecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20key%20priority.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20in%20that%20context%20today%20that%20several%20members%20condemned%20it%2C%20saying%20it%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20happened.%20Food%20passing%20through%20the%20Black%20Sea%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20stopped%20or%20suspended%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20reporters.%20Russia%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20was%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20deal%20that%20allowed%20transport%20of%20grain%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20parts%20of%20Africa%20through%20the%20Black%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20continuing%20divisions%20over%20the%20language%20on%20Ukraine%20makes%20it%20likely%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20common%20Delhi%20declaration%20at%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20pointed%20out%20that%20Russia%20and%20China%20had%20effectively%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20language%20agreed%20in%20Bali