he%20Indian%20railway%20ministry%20was%20compelled%20to%20honour%20the%20joint%20venture%20in%20its%20original%20form%20thanks%20to%20looming%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2018%2C%20the%20Indian%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Limited%20has%20said%20in%20its%20disclosure%20that%20the%20RVNL%2C%20its%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiary%20Kinet%20Railway%20Solutions%20Limited%2C%20the%20Russian%20company%20Metrowagonmash%20and%20a%20joint%20stock%20company%20Locomotive%20Electronic%20Systems%20have%20signed%20a%20share%20purchase%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMetrowagonmash%20is%20an%20engineering%20company%20based%20at%20Mytishchi%20in%20Russia%2C%20and%20specialises%20in%20transport%20building.%20It%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20TMH%20Group%2C%20the%20largest%20manufacturer%20of%20locomotive%20and%20rail%20equipment%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20joint%20venture%20deal%2C%20reports%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20RVNL%20has%20a%20minority%20stake%20of%2025%25%2C%20while%20Metrowagonmash%20retains%20a%20majority%20stake%20of%2070%25.%20Another%205%25%20is%20held%20by%20Locomotive%20Electronic%20Systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERVNL%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20insistence%20that%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20joint%20venture%20be%20drastically%20flipped%20to%20give%20it%2069%25%20majority%20shareholding%20had%20pushed%20the%20understanding%20into%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERVNL%20had%20argued%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20because%20multiple%20spare%20parts%20for%20the%20trains%20would%20have%20to%20be%20imported%20from%20western%20European%20and%20American%20counterparts%2C%20majority%20stake-holding%20on%20its%20part%20will%20lead%20to%20confidence%20among%20sellers%20considering%20that%20Russia%20had%20lost%20the%20goodwill%20of%20the%20west%20over%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Frailways%2Fvande-bharat-sleeper-trains-plan-hits-a-snag%2Farticleshow%2F101089838.cms%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20senior%20TMH%20officials%20as%20having%20said%20then%20that%20RVNL%E2%80%99s%20demand%20was%C2%A0in%20violation%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cirrevocable%20and%20binding%20agreement%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20two%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RVNL%20and%20Metrowagonmash%20consortium%20had%20won%20a%20a%20Rs%2040%2C000-crore%20supply%20and%20maintenance%20contract%20for%20120%20of%20200%20Vande%20Bharat%20sleeper%20trains.%20Each%20costs%20Rs%20120%20crores.%20The%20consortium%20will%20have%20to%20maintain%20these%20trains%20for%2035%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rift%20had%20delayed%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20it%20had%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20June%202025%20deadline%2C%20by%20when%20the%20consortium%20has%20to%20present%20the%20first%20two%20prototype%20trains%20for%20testing%20and%20trials%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20prodded%20RVNL%20to%20accept%20the%20current%20terms%20and%20sign%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20prototypes%20are%20approved%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%2C%20every%20year%2012%20to%2018%20trains%20will%20be%20manufactured.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689757211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F20150450%2FVande-Bharat1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvande-bharat-rail-vikas-nigam-india-russia-joint-venture%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22the%20Indian%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Limited%20had%20earlier%20been%20pressing%20for%20a%20higher%20share%20in%20the%20deal%20to%20supply%20120%20Vande%20Bharat%20sleeper%20trains%20and%20maintain%20them%20for%2035%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvande-bharat