E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20this%20would%20ensure%20that%20two%20communities%20stay%20together.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20ensure%20(good)%20intentions%20(are%20kept).%20Hindus%20tend%20to%20flee%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandey%20made%20these%20comments%20during%20her%20visit%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20Munshi%20Purwa%20area%20to%20look%20into%20complaints%20of%20encroachment%20near%20a%20Hindu%20shrine.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20received%20a%20complaint%20from%20an%20elderly%20man%20about%20a%20shrine%20and%20a%20well%20in%20Munshi%20Purwa%20being%20occupied%20by%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20So%20I%20reached%20here.%20They%20have%20occupied%20the%20well%20and%20dumped%20garbage%20upon%20it.%20Someone%20has%20made%20a%20window%20and%20a%20gate%20near%20the%20shrine.%20This%20shows%20bad%20intentions%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pandey%20said%20she%20had%20no%20problem%20with%20Muslims%2C%20she%20was%20worried%20about%20their%20%E2%80%9Cintentions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20(Muslims)%20caused%20so%20much%20(trouble)%20that%20Hindus%20left%20(this%20place).%20Don%E2%80%99t%20touch%20the%20shrine.%20The%20shrine%20belongs%20to%20us.%20It%20will%20remain%20where%20it%20is.%20(But%20instead)%20you%20make%20a%20door%20or%20a%20window%20near%20it%2C%20(even)%20relieve%20yourself%20(there).%20This%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20where%20Pandey%20can%20be%20heard%20making%20controversial%20remarks%20also%20surfaced.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20cleaning%20happen%3F%20Hindus%20think%20that%20they%20(Muslims)%20are%20paying%20more%20money%2C%20sell%20off%20the%20house%20and%20leave.%20They%20(Muslims)%20have%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20can%20be%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20mayor%20visited%20the%20spot%2C%20about%20100-200%20people%20also%20reached%20there.%20The%20well%20was%20covered%20with%20construction%20debris%20and%20the%20occupants%20had%20extended%20the%20awnings%20(of%20their%20house)%20and%20were%20trying%20to%20occupy%20the%20entire%20premises.%20She%20directed%20the%20junior%20engineer%20to%20probe%20the%20matter.%20If%20the%20work%20is%20illegal%2C%20it%20will%20stop.%20Otherwise%2C%20no%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20media%20in-charge%20Prashant%20Shukla%20told%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Pandey%20has%20found%20herself%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20controversy.%20The%20BJP%20leader%E2%80%99s%20demolition%20drive%20against%20alleged%20encroachments%20in%20Saket%20Nagar%20last%20month%20led%20to%20several%20meat%20and%20fish%20shops%20being%20removed%2C%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20While%20the%20authorities%20claimed%20the%20establishments%20were%20illegal%2C%20the%20action%20drew%20protests%20from%20their%20owners%2C%20who%20claimed%20they%20had%20been%20operating%20in%20the%20area%20for%20years%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandey%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkanpur-mayor-in-trouble-over-pic-case-filed-for-violating-secret-ballot-2778411%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKanpur%2520Mayor%2520Pramila%2520Pandey%2520created%2CSchool%2520polling%2520booth%2520in%2520Kanpur.%5C%22%3Ebooked%20for%20allegedly%20clicking%20pictures%20inside%20a%20polling%20booth%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sharing%20them%20on%20WhatsApp%20during%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689752719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19121406%2FF1PDYO4agAA_tfv.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkanpurs-bjp-mayor-thinks-hindus-muslims-shouldnt-be-allowed-to-buy-each-others-houses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayor%20Pramila%2