ss%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20a%20well%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%20that%20was%20stuck%20in%20it%20for%20days.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Meghana%20Pemmaiah%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20forest%20department%20is%20always%20short%20of%20such%20rescuers%20and%20Meghana%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20has%20been%20helping%20us%20in%20missions.%20The%20animals%20are%20usually%20found%20in%20encroached%20forest%20land%2C%20stuck%20in%20wells%2C%20and%20sometimes%20in%20households.%20This%20puts%20the%20life%20of%20the%20animal%20and%20the%20surrounding%20people%20in%20jeopardy.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20plan%20and%20execute%20everything%20very%20carefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dangerous%20yet%20thrilling%20incident%20recently%2C%20Meghana%20had%20to%20jump%20into%20a%2020-feet-deep%20well%20at%20Niddodi%20in%20Dakshina%20Kannada%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%20stuck%20in%20it%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20well%20was%20quite%20deep%20and%20we%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20leopardess.%20The%20only%20option%20was%20to%20jump%20inside%20to%20sedate%20her%20and%20carry%20her%20up.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20I%20was%20put%20in%20a%20cage%20and%20lowered%20into%20the%20well.%20I%20darted%20at%20the%20leopardess%20at%20close%20range%20and%20waited%20until%20she%20was%20sedated.%20I%20dragged%20her%20into%20my%20cage%20afterwards%20and%20the%20team%20pulled%20us%20both%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghana%20took%20the%20animal%20under%20her%20care%2C%20examining%20it%20for%20injuries%20and%20providing%20treatment.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20animals%20are%20kept%20under%20observation.%20When%20they%20become%20fit%2C%20we%20take%20them%20to%20their%20real%20home%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wilderness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20animal-human%20conflict%20regularly%3C%2F