%20the%20memories%20of%20his%20city%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20would%20go%20on%20to%20influence%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20local%20culture%20in%20numerous%20ways.%20For%20one%2C%20Wajid%20Ali%20introduced%20sports%20like%20kite-flying%20and%20cock-fighting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20poetry%20in%20the%20region.%20Among%20these%20notable%20contributions%20was%20food%2C%20namely%2C%20biryani.%20So%20what%20has%20been%20embraced%20today%20as%20Kolkata%20biryani%20in%20fact%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20city%20of%20%3Cem%3Enawabs%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Manzilat%20Fatima%2C%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20the%20king%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20characteristic%20of%20Awadh%20biryani%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20one.%20They%20are%20like%20cousins%20of%20one%20family.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manzilat%20Fatima%20is%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManzilat%20Fatima%20is%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%2055-year-old%20has%20run%20Manzilat%E2%80%99s%2C%20a%20home%20diner%20to%20keep%20the%20legacy%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20her%20to%20understand%20the%20history%20and%20relevance%20of%20the%20food%20brought%20to%20the%20city%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Enawab%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERoyal%20cousins%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F231208%2Findia-unknown-history-kebab-how-recipe-food-tunde-kebabs-nawab-lucknow-wajid-ali%2F%5C%22%3EWajid%20Ali%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20patron%20of%20art%2C%20music%2C%20poetry%2C%20drama%2C%20and%20gastronomy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20art%20of%20cooking%20and%20relishing%20good%20food.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20he%20was%20not%20a%20%3Cem%3EBadshah%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emperor)%20anymore%2C%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%20was%20born%20a%20%3Cem%3Enawab%3C%2Fem%3E.%20His%20love%20for%20gastronomy%20shaped%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270232%2Fbest-biryani-places-in-india-iconic-restaurants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucknowi%20biryani%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20came%20to%20Kolkata.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20potatoes%2C%20it%20became%20what%20we%20today%20relish%20as%20Kolkata%20biryani%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20potatoes%20were%20considered%20a%20%3Cem%3Enayab%3C%2Fem%3E%20(exotic)%20delicacy.%20Although%20common%20people%20could%20not%20afford%20them%2C%20the%20vegetable%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20royal%20kitchens.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20it%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20absorb%20all%20aromas%20of%20spices%2C%20it%20enhances%20the%20flavours%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20added%20to%20the%20dish.%20It%20was%20readily%20accepted%20by%20the%20King%20and%20the%20people.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20when%20his%20%3Cem%3Emulazim%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(workers)%20were%20jobless%2C%20they%20went%20to%20cities%20and%20this%20biryani%20was%20spread%20in%20Kolkata%20city%20and%20became%20popular%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manzilat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Manzilat's%20(%40manzilats)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20what%20sets%20the%20Awadhi%20and%20Kolkata%20biryani%20apart%20from%20the%20rest.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20nawabs%20were%20of%20%3Cem%3Enazuk%20mizaz%20%3C%2Fem%3E(delicate%20nature)%2C%20spicy%20food%20did%20not%20suit%20their%20palate.%20This%20makes%20the%20Aw