e%20of%20delicacies%20including%20Lakhnawai%20Mutton%20Yakhni%20Pulao%2C%20Chicken%20Nawabi%20Chaanp%2C%20Ulta%20Tawa%20Paratha%2C%20Fish%20Chatpata%20Handi%20Kabab%2C%20Chicken%20Lazeez%20Shami%20Kabab%2C%20and%20Shahi%20Badam%20Firni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Kolkata%20Food%20Lovers%20(%40kolkatafoodlovers)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearnt%20cooking%20through%20letters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzilat%20recalls%20that%20when%20she%20started%20cooking%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20she%20was%20not%20interested%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20living%20with%20my%20father%20in%20Aligarh.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20ordering%20food%20from%20outside%20was%20not%20as%20relevant%20as%20it%20is%20today.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20cook%20along%20with%20a%20helper%20and%20would%20serve%20%3Cem%3Ekacha%20pakka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(half-cooked)%20food%20to%20my%20father.%20Sometimes%2C%20there%20would%20be%20more%20water%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekhichadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20sometimes%20rice%20would%20be%20half-cooked.%20I%20would%20fail%20to%20make%20a%20perfect%20meal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20her%20mother%20would%20come%20to%20her%20rescue.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20used%20to%20write%20letters%20to%20us%20from%20Kolkata.%20In%20those%20letters%2C%20she%20would%20write%20a%20recipe%20and%20cooking%20method%20for%20me%20in%20Urdu.%20During%20vacations%20when%20we%20would%20be%20home%2C%20I%20used%20to%20learn%20from%20her.%20The%20first%20thing%20I%20learnt%20from%20her%20was%20%3Cem%3Eshami%20kabab%3C%2Fem%3E.%20My%20father%20relished%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20married%2C%20Manzilat%20settled%20in%20Kolkata.%20She%20loved%20to%20host%20guests%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20friends%20of%20her%20children.%20Through%20cooking%20over%20the%20years%2C%20she%20developed%20an%20immense%20interest%20in%20food.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20knew%20that%20I%20would%20build%20a%20career%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-300x157.jpg%20300