ues%20for%20others%20to%20grow%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2057-year-old%20Apurva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20quit%20and%20move%20into%20the%20social%20sector%2C%20Apurva%20expressed%20this%20desire%20to%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aazol%20sells%20various%20types%20of%20authentic%20Maharashtrian%20snacks%20and%20spices%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faazol-3-1688737533-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323127%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20works%20with%201%2C000%2B%20SHG%20workers%20to%20source%20authentic%20Maharashtrian%20snacks%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Apurva%20Purohit%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20was%20very%20happy%20in%20my%20career%2C%20the%20urge%20was%20always%20there.%20However%2C%20when%20we%20were%20home%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20became%20stronger.%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20think.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20started%20to%20question%20whether%20what%20I%20am%20doing%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20social%20divide%20of%20our%20country%20became%20so%20much%20more%20visible.%20I%20st